2
0:00:15.388,000 --> 0:00:16,000
of creative expression,

3
0:00:17.042,000 --> 0:00:18,000
but for the most part,

4
0:00:18.613,000 --> 0:00:2,000
that expression is confined to the screens

5
0:00:20.778,000 --> 0:00:22,000
of our laptops and mobile phones.

6
0:00:23.196,000 --> 0:00:25,000
And I'd like to tell you a story about

7
0:00:25.396,000 --> 0:00:26,000
bringing this power of the computer

8
0:00:27.352,000 --> 0:00:29,000
to move things around and interact with us

9
0:00:29.722,000 --> 0:00:31,000
off of the screen and into the physical world

10
0:00:32.635,000 --> 0:00:33,000
in which we live.

11
