12
0:00:35.442,000 --> 0:00:37,000
a luxury fashion store called Barneys New York,

13
0:00:37.928,000 --> 0:00:38,000
and the next thing I knew,

14
0:00:39.192,000 --> 0:00:41,000
I was designing storefront kinetic sculptures

15
